title: GCP Storage Agents - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: The GCP Storage agents collect and forward batches of files from specified buckets in the Google Cloud Platform, and are available in batch workflow configurations. This section contains the following subsections: GCP Storage Collection Agent GCP Storage Forwarding Agent
